---
---
<section id="recursos" class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-beige">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="inline-block text-[0.7rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-rose font-medium mb-3.5">
        Herramientas para ti
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl lg:text-[3rem] font-normal text-brown-dark leading-[1.2] mb-4">
        Guías y recursos
      </h2>
      <div class="w-[60px] h-0.5 bg-rose rounded-sm my-5 mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-[0.95rem] text-text-soft leading-[1.75] font-light max-w-[560px]">
        Materiales diseñados para que puedas empezar hoy tu camino de transformación.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-12" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-8 text-center border border-beige-dark transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(107,78,61,0.1)] flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="text-[2.4rem] mb-4">📖</div>
        <div class="text-[0.68rem] tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-rose font-medium mb-2.5">Guía gratuita</div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-medium text-brown-dark mb-3 leading-[1.3]">Hábitos diarios con el Método NEURO</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-text-soft leading-[1.65] font-light mb-5 flex-1">Rutina completa para la mujer femenina, poderosa y libre. 8 páginas de transformación.</p>
        <a href="/documentos/guia-de-habitos.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block border-[1.5px] border-rose text-rose px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-rose hover:text-white">Descargar gratis</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-8 text-center border border-beige-dark transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(107,78,61,0.1)] flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="text-[2.4rem] mb-4">🧠</div>
        <div class="text-[0.68rem] tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-rose font-medium mb-2.5">Plantilla</div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-medium text-brown-dark mb-3 leading-[1.3]">Diario emocional NEURO</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-text-soft leading-[1.65] font-light mb-5 flex-1">Registra tus emociones diarias aplicando los 5 pasos del método para crear conciencia real.</p>
        <a href="/documentos/diario-emocional.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block border-[1.5px] border-rose text-rose px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-rose hover:text-white">Obtener plantilla</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-8 text-center border border-beige-dark transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(107,78,61,0.1)] flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="text-[2.4rem] mb-4">💌</div>
        <div class="text-[0.68rem] tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-rose font-medium mb-2.5">Ejercicio</div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-medium text-brown-dark mb-3 leading-[1.3]">Carta a ti misma</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-text-soft leading-[1.65] font-light mb-5 flex-1">Guía paso a paso para escribirte desde tus fortalezas. El ejercicio más transformador del método.</p>
        <a href="/documentos/carta-a-mi-misma.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block border-[1.5px] border-rose text-rose px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-rose hover:text-white">Quiero este ejercicio</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-8 text-center border border-beige-dark transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(107,78,61,0.1)] flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="text-[2.4rem] mb-4">🌬️</div>
        <div class="text-[0.68rem] tracking-[0.16em] uppercase text-rose font-medium mb-2.5">Audio guiado</div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-medium text-brown-dark mb-3 leading-[1.3]">Respiración para sanar</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-text-soft leading-[1.65] font-light mb-5 flex-1">Técnica de respiración diafragmática guiada. Para el estrés crónico y la ansiedad diaria.</p>
        <a href="/respiracion" class="inline-block border-[1.5px] border-rose text-rose px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-rose hover:text-white">Realizar Ejercicio</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
